                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1407-18420404 t18420404-1407-punishment-256"></join>Confined Eighteen Months</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Justice Erskine.</hi>
